{"tid":1804028,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"笑死，驚甴係唔係以為自己好醒，好識玩公關","createTime":"2019-12-30T16:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T16:10:54.000Z","uid":284540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f244ffd744908bc653d66395f8c1b4be14e9f34","tid":1804028,"uid":284540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"警甴今朝拎張圖叫民陣解釋，而家又話歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆，係咪以為自己好醒，成功分化到和理非同勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂呀唔好咁搞笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>警：歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆 鼓吹除夕夜犯法與黑社會無異</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張與民陣元旦遊行海報類似，惟寫有「毋忘報仇，全城裝修」的圖片，民陣澄清與其組織無關。警方下午與記者會中歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆。<br />\n警方指，留意到有人鼓吹於除夕夜進行犯法行為，形容有關動作為毫無道德的黑社會手段，處方將主動執法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tmhk.org/2019/12/30/警：歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆-鼓吹除夕夜犯法與黑社會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2F2019%2F12%2F30%2F%E8%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E8%88%87%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%89%B2%E8%93%86-%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%95%E5%A4%9C%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95%E8%88%87%E9%BB%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=b73c9b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tmhk.org/2019/12/30/警：歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆-鼓吹除夕夜犯法與黑社會/</a><br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>民陣facebook回應：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n民陣就假海報作出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n民陣昨日收到警方傳來一張假海報，並聲稱有人篡改民陣就元旦遊行的海報設計，改為呼籲抗爭者於 1 月 1 日進行「全城裝修」。<br />\n<br />\n民陣在警隊轉發海報予我方前，民陣從未於各 Telegram 公海、討論區發現相關改圖。根據傳媒報導，相關海報是在建制派支援者的社群網絡中開始流傳。民陣質疑警隊發出的假海報的來源。<br />\n<br />\n今日警方向民陣副召集人陳皓桓發出警告，指民陣如不作出澄清，或將涉嫌煽動。民陣在此清晰表示，被刪改海報上的內容違背了我們發起遊行的原意，作為「受害」一方，民陣竟再被警方威脅，實在是非常離譜，警隊應主動調查假海報來源，例如從上載假海報的建制派人士開始查起，而非要求我們作出澄清。<br />\n<br />\n警隊在今日的四時記者會上更稱「歡迎民陣與暴力割席」，民陣對相關言論百思不得其解，唯有在此重申，我們一定會與警察的暴力割席，自六月十二日中信鎮壓事件及其後至今的所有警暴，民陣都強烈、清晰地反對，而今日民陣在記者會就假海報的說明，是對 A 貨割席，不要搞錯。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019 年 12 月 30 日"},{"pid":"71930d1c4a6cbf545b249c9cef5b5ff24df77b51","tid":1804028,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=b6ea844c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=ed1cd40d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要29000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=986c4021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadl